Key VPS Features

More Compute Power for Less Money

Best thing about Contabo VPS? Price efficiency! Starting from 4.99 you get your own virtual server with an operating system of your choice and full root access. A Virtual Private Server is a great way to get an independent computing instance at an unmatched price point.

Storage Customization

You can choose the type of storage that goes with each VPS. Go with a super fast NVMe storage with over 1,000,000 IOPS or a large SSD drive if space is more important than speed for you. If you can't decide, you can have both thanks to NVMe Storage Expansion Add-On

More Traffic then You Will Ever Need

Each VPS comes with 32 TB of outgoing and unlimited incoming traffic included with a connection speed between 200 Mbit/s and 1 Gbit/s. In reality this is equal to unlimited traffic for 99.98% of our customers. Unlike some of our competitors, at Contabo we will never charge you extra for incoming or outgoing data transfer on your Virtual Private Server.

Quick Provisioning

Every day we provision hundreds of VPS with an average time of 20 minutes. Make sure to pay for Virtual Private Server with credit card so that we can provision it right away without waiting for money to arrive.
